This paper is about hyperparameter tuning for machine learning algorithms, which is a topic that falls under the umbrella of machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other possible categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics).
